    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > ABOUT THE GAME [/]<br>In the past of this world, civilization reached a high level of social and technical development, but then the world experienced a global catastrophe, the fall of the asteroid and the subsequent extraterrestrial pandemic as a result of which civilization and most of the wealth it created were destroyed. A suitable conglomerate of communities has been created on habitable territory; a more or less stable balance of forces has developed. But, the impact of the pandemic is only growing, the confrontation between survivors and those affected by the disease reaches a critical point. You have to survive in the new world. Create tools, fight unpredictable wildlife, infected animals and survivors.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Key Features: [/]<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> Abandoned, partially destroyed cities, enterprises, military facilities.<br></li><li> The action takes place in a fictional world of the future, where nature after the fall of the asteroid took its toll. A constant danger awaits at every corner: gangs, infected animals and people.<br></li><li> Realistic firearms and melee weapons, as well as close combat.<br></li><li> Construction run away, defenses, bases.<br></li><li> Join groups, clans and try to survive in this world unpredictable for events<br></li><li> Multiplayer sandbox mode;<br></li><li> Day-night cycle and dynamic weather;<br></li><li> Change in appearance (clothes, weapons) and armor;<br></li><li> The mechanics of the character’s state (bleeding, wound, hunger, thirst); [/]</li></ul></h2></h2>",
